import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Text,
  Center,
  VStack,
  Input,
  Flex,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";

export const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Flex
      width="100vw"
      height="100vh"
      bgColor="#121214"
      direction="column"
      justify="center"
      align="center"
    >
      <Text color="#FF577F">Kenzie Hub</Text>
      <VStack>
        <Box w="100%">
          <Text color="#F8F9FA" fontSize="sm" alignItem="left">
            Email
          </Text>
        </Box>
        <Input placeholder="Digite seu email" />
        <Input placeholder="Digite sua senha" />
      </VStack>
    </Flex>
  );
};
